metadata.name: Deep Electric Swamp
metadata.description:
The dimensions have fractured in the swamp, wet, elastic, vegetation and animals take plastic and unreal forms, the environment is charged with electrical energies and has awakened entities seeking new bodies.
The high voltage towers protect the castle born from the deep residues of ancient and sacred memories. 
Pollution is natural, it has broken new limits, and it will always be with us. 

Animated landscape made from 3D sculptures made in VR + artificial intelligence elements + Blender.
1920x1080px 280 frames.
Whoever buys this piece can ask me for the 4K version.
